    "description": "游戏特点:<br>在这座宅邸中，每一个细微的声音都会引发你的恐惧，而任何超自然现象都会让你感到焦虑和不安。然而，这座看似废弃已久的房子里电力仍然运转。光是唯一能让你平静下来的东西，它让你能够观察并继续前行。但这真的能帮到你吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.poster.avif?t=1770123315\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.webm?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fe3ac3182624830cb046c15b0ede59dd.mp4?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏玩法:<br>你将探索这座宅邸，收集有用的物品并解开谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.poster.avif?t=1770123315\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.webm?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/f4884f9293bb6382194f9e534ceb4b09.mp4?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不要期待轻松的漫步——每一个角落后可能都潜藏着危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/66fd7fbb5a29663fd1f1500f1d34a096.poster.avif?t=1770123315\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/66fd7fbb5a29663fd1f1500f1d34a096.webm?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/66fd7fbb5a29663fd1f1500f1d34a096.mp4?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>剧情:<br>你在沙发上醒来，不知道自己是如何来到这里，也不清楚这是个什么地方。在稍微探索了一下房间后，你发现了一篇关于一个神秘失踪的家庭的文章。这与主角有什么关系，还是他只是一个随机的受害者？你需要找到这些问题的答案。游戏中将有多个结局，而选择权在你手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fc22b1eba5241f916e0c2373b6591224.poster.avif?t=1770123315\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fc22b1eba5241f916e0c2373b6591224.webm?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015350/extras/fc22b1eba5241f916e0c2373b6591224.mp4?t=1770123315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你准备好进入Echoes Of Dread的世界，揭开它所有黑暗的秘密了吗？",
